  "detailed_description": "<strong>Whether you're a 60s rolling stone, a 70s disco queen, an 80's big hair rocker or just a walking music database, prove your skills and steal the scene in this party game. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/e81f0ec2a0d246ba7fbbdf9e59a45408.poster.avif?t=1774002025\" width=614 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/e81f0ec2a0d246ba7fbbdf9e59a45408.webm?t=1774002025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/e81f0ec2a0d246ba7fbbdf9e59a45408.mp4?t=1774002025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step 1. Along with up to 8 players (minimum 2), you can use your phone or tablet as a game controller and join your room.<br><br>When all the players joined, hit “Start” and enjoy a rondom playlist. If you want to choose your playlist, try one of our <strong>VIP</strong> passes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/376b7e08e979b36fe8ea9f070adb5671.poster.avif?t=1774002025\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/376b7e08e979b36fe8ea9f070adb5671.webm?t=1774002025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Step 2. Listen to the song sample and enter on your game controller of choise a fake lyric to fit the snippet and fool the other players.<br><br>Vote your favorite lyric - you’ll get a “thanks” if you vote a friends’ lyric, but keep in mind that the truth always makes you a winner.<br><br>Step 3. T-t-t-tie breaker! Last round is a Speed Round. Answer correctly and you get points for each second left on the clock.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/1377d952e61145bb37b7eebdee96257a.apng?t=1774002025\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/1377d952e61145bb37b7eebdee96257a.poster.avif?t=1774002025\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=60 /></picture></span><br><br>Try to get as many points as you can, but remember to have fun!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Whether you're a 60s rolling stone, a 70s disco queen, an 80's big hair rocker or just a walking music database, prove your skills and steal the scene in this party game. </strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/e81f0ec2a0d246ba7fbbdf9e59a45408.poster.avif?t=1774002025\" width=614 height=110 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/e81f0ec2a0d246ba7fbbdf9e59a45408.webm?t=1774002025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/e81f0ec2a0d246ba7fbbdf9e59a45408.mp4?t=1774002025\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Step 1. Along with up to 8 players (minimum 2), you can use your phone or tablet as a game controller and join your room.<br><br>When all the players joined, hit “Start” and enjoy a rondom playlist. If you want to choose your playlist, try one of our <strong>VIP</strong> passes.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/376b7e08e979b36fe8ea9f070adb5671.poster.avif?t=1774002025\" width=614 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/376b7e08e979b36fe8ea9f070adb5671.webm?t=1774002025\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>Step 2. Listen to the song sample and enter on your game controller of choise a fake lyric to fit the snippet and fool the other players.<br><br>Vote your favorite lyric - you’ll get a “thanks” if you vote a friends’ lyric, but keep in mind that the truth always makes you a winner.<br><br>Step 3. T-t-t-tie breaker! Last round is a Speed Round. Answer correctly and you get points for each second left on the clock.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/1377d952e61145bb37b7eebdee96257a.apng?t=1774002025\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1315390/extras/1377d952e61145bb37b7eebdee96257a.poster.avif?t=1774002025\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=60 /></picture></span><br><br>Try to get as many points as you can, but remember to have fun!",
